PART 8: c5 varies but K is constant - the cancellation
============================================================
  n=7: c3=14, C(c3,2)=91, K=-126
  Formula: ov1 + ov2 = (c5 + 126)/2
  And disj = 91 - (c5 + 126)/2 = 91 + 63 - c5/2 = 28 - (c5-126)/2

  Verification on random regular n=7 tournaments:
